'''Dragon masks''' are possible rewards from [[Treasure Trails]] and can be worn in the head slot. [[Chromatic dragon]] masks can be obtained from [[Clue scroll (hard)|hard]] Treasure Trails, while [[metal dragon|metal]] and [[lava dragon]] masks can be obtained from [[Clue scroll (elite)|elite]] Treasure Trails.

All of the dragon masks can be stored independently from each other in the [[treasure chest]] of a player's [[costume room]].

